WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.700
After documentation exists, BharatDoc keeps review in the doctor's hands.

00:05.700 --> 00:11.600
From the dashboard, the doctor opens a test consultation and switches between transcript and summary.

00:11.600 --> 00:18.300
The summary is editable, so corrections can be made before anything is finalized.

00:18.300 --> 00:24.500
Here the doctor adds a short review note and saves the updated summary.

00:24.500 --> 00:31.000
Once the summary is saved, BharatDoc can generate a Patient ID PDF for clinic use.

00:31.000 --> 00:36.800
The PDF panel confirms when the file is ready and provides an open button for the generated document.

00:36.800 --> 00:39.864
This shows current product behavior: review, edit, save, and prepare documentation for use.
